---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Writing Manifesto | Tower Notes"
  description="The editorial and factual rules behind Tower Notes."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Manifesto</p>
    <h1>写作和维护原则</h1>
    <p>高质量但失真，比普通内容更危险。这个站默认怀疑一切未被证实的漂亮说法。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-grid">
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>1. Primary first</h2>
      <p>优先官方文档、论文、源码、技术博客。二手解读只能做线索，不能直接当依据。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>2. Separate facts from judgment</h2>
      <p>事实要可核验；判断要明确写出依据和适用边界，不能混成一句“我觉得”。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>3. Timestamp everything</h2>
      <p>AI Infra 和 agent 变化快。每篇内容都标记访问时间和更新时间，过期内容要修订。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>4. Publish less, mean more</h2>
      <p>宁可少发，也不发“看起来很懂”的错结论。复利建立在可信度上，不在频率上。</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
